- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the nefarious use of fake accounts on social media and its impact on society. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category as the paper touches upon the issue of impersonation and fake accounts, which are security concerns on social media platforms. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is a possible category as the paper analyzes the engagement behavior of impersonators on Instagram, which is related to social and behavioral sciences. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper collects data on comments and likes on Instagram posts, which involves multimedia content.
